OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPersil advert banned for   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmisleading green claims    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Unilever's advert for one of its       
OL,6, laundry detergents, Persil, has been   
OL,7, banned for being misleading about its  
OL,8, environmental benefits.                
OL,10,FThe television advert said Persil was  
OL,11,F"kinder to our planet", and featured   
OL,12,Fchildren picking up litter on a beach. 
OL,14,FThe Advertising Standards Authority    
OL,15,F(ASA) said the advert's claim was      
OL,16,Funsubstantiated.                       
OL,18,FUnilever, which owns brands including  
OL,19,FHellmann's and Dove, said it is        
OL,20,F"disappointed" with the result.        
